            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Once your potatoes have had an initial 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven, stir your <strong>sambal oelek </strong>through the potatoes and push them to one side</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and <strong>chopped green beans</strong> to the other side of the tray[s] and return to the oven for 7-8 min or until the veg has cooked through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1723198660806-x200.jpg",
