            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the <strong>ketjap manis sauce</strong> and cook for a further 2 min or until sticky and coated – this is your<strong> sticky chicken ayam ketjap manis</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
