    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky chicken ayam ketjap manis </strong>with the <strong>sambal potatoes</strong> and <strong>roasted veg</strong> to one side</p><p>Spoon over any <strong>remaining ketjap manis sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>crispy lime leaf & garlic</strong> and the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
